ZH: 他总是喜欢摆布我们。
EN: He always likes to manipulate us.

ZH: 她通过摆布他人来控制局面。
EN: She controls the situation by manipulating others.

ZH: 我不喜欢被别人摆布。
EN: I don't like being manipulated by others.

ZH: 他把整个团队摆布在手中。
EN: He has the whole team under his control.

ZH: 她总是善于摆布事物的发展。
EN: She is always good at manipulating the development of things.

ZH: 我们不应该被别人摆布。
EN: We should not be manipulated by others.

ZH: 他用手上的权力来摆布别人。
EN: He uses his power to manipulate others.

ZH: 她通过眼泪来摆布他们。
EN: She manipulates them through her tears.

ZH: 我们不能任由别人摆布。
EN: We cannot allow others to manipulate us.

ZH: 他操纵新闻来摆布公众的情绪。
EN: He manipulates the news to manipulate the emotions of the public.

ZH: 他善于摆布局势。
EN: He is good at manipulating the situation.

ZH: 她总是能够摆布他人的想法。
EN: She is always able to manipulate others' thoughts.

ZH: 这个人擅长摆布别人的感情。
EN: This person is good at manipulating others' emotions.

ZH: 他总是喜欢摆布别人的人生。
EN: He always likes to manipulate others' lives.

ZH: 她通过伪装来摆布他人。
EN: She manipulates others by disguising herself.

ZH: 他总是善于摆布周围的一切。
EN: He is always good at manipulating everything around him.

ZH: 她利用人们的软弱来摆布他们。
EN: She uses people's weaknesses to manipulate them.

ZH: 不要被任何人摆布。
EN: Don't be manipulated by anyone.

ZH: 他通过威胁来摆布别人。
EN: He manipulates others through threats.

ZH: 她总是能够巧妙地摆布別人。
EN: She is always able to deftly manipulate others.
